SOLAR — UI sound cues
======================

The UI sound effects in this directory are drawn from the "minimal" pack of
uisfx by Romain Simon.

  Source : https://github.com/romainsimon/uisfx
  Audio  : CC0 1.0 Universal (public domain dedication) — no attribution required
  Code   : MIT (the uisfx runtime; not used here — we ship a small local manager)

Because the audio is released under CC0, no attribution is legally required.
This NOTICE is a courtesy credit recording provenance.

Files used (semantic cue -> file):
  menu / palette open   -> open.{mp3,ogg}
  toggle on             -> toggle-on.{mp3,ogg}
  toggle off            -> toggle-off.{mp3,ogg}
  success / commit      -> success.{mp3,ogg}
  error / access-denied -> error.{mp3,ogg}
  notify / silent-hit   -> notification.{mp3,ogg}
  select (report/entity)-> select.{mp3,ogg}

Only these curated cues are copied in. The full 78-cue taxonomy and the other
packs (organic, mechanical, cinematic) were auditioned and deliberately not
shipped — "minimal" was chosen for the most restrained, professional tone.

Sound is always supplementary. It reinforces visible feedback and is never the
sole signal for any state. A persistent mute preference is provided.
